<h6 class="kicker">Op-Ed Columnist</h6>
<h1 class="articleHeadline"><NYT_HEADLINE  version="1.0" type=" ">The Fragile Community</NYT_HEADLINE></h1>
<NYT_BYLINE >	<h6 class="byline">By <a href="http://topics.nytimes.com/top/opinion/editorialsandoped/oped/columnists/davidbrooks/index.html?inline=nyt-per" title="More Articles by David Brooks" class="meta-per">DAVID BROOKS</a></h6>
