  <div style="padding:7px 9px 0;background:#fff">
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;line-height:24px; margin:0;padding:0 0 4px;"><a style="color:#365db5;" target="_blank" href="http://www.nytimes.com/adx/bin/adx_click.html?type=goto&opzn&page=www.nytimes.com/yr/mo/day/opinion/30brooks.html&pos=Box1&sn2=8fd7dcd8/4eee80ef&sn1=551dfcaf/fecc43b4&camp=NYT2010_marketingmodule&ad=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-121&goto=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/12/16/2010-in-the-rearview-mirror/%3Fex=1308632400%26en=dad7319a2a9e6e6e%26ei=5087%26WT.mc_id=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-1210-HDR%26WT.mc_ev=click">2010, in the rearview mirror</a></h2>
      <p style="margin:0 0 3px; padding:0;font-size: 11px;"><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/adx/bin/adx_click.html?type=goto&opzn&page=www.nytimes.com/yr/mo/day/opinion/30brooks.html&pos=Box1&sn2=8fd7dcd8/4eee80ef&sn1=be6188c5/760a1a14&camp=NYT2010_marketingmodule&ad=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-121&goto=http://www.nytimes.com/pages/arts/index.html%3FWT.mc_id=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-1210-URL%26WT.mc_ev=click" target="_blank" style="font-size:11px;margin:3px 0;padding:0;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;  color:#000; text-transform:uppercase;">Also in Arts &raquo;</a></p>
      <ul style="font-size:12px;margin:0; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom:1px solid #ccc;" class="refer">
        <li style="font-size:12px"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.nytimes.com/adx/bin/adx_click.html?type=goto&opzn&page=www.nytimes.com/yr/mo/day/opinion/30brooks.html&pos=Box1&sn2=8fd7dcd8/4eee80ef&sn1=be6188c5/760a1a14&camp=NYT2010_marketingmodule&ad=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-121&goto=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/19/books/review/Keillor-t.html%3Fex=1308632400%26en=45d6828780fdd639%26ei=5087%26WT.mc_id=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-1210-L1%26WT.mc_ev=click">Garrison Keillor reviews "Autobiography of Mark Twain"</a></li>
        <li style="font-size:12px"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.nytimes.com/adx/bin/adx_click.html?type=goto&opzn&page=www.nytimes.com/yr/mo/day/opinion/30brooks.html&pos=Box1&sn2=8fd7dcd8/4eee80ef&sn1=be6188c5/760a1a14&camp=NYT2010_marketingmodule&ad=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-121&goto=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/12/books/review/10-best-books-of-2010.html%3Fex=1308632400%26en=b165a5583548d833%26ei=5087%26WT.mc_id=AR-D-I-NYT-MOD-MOD-M181a-ROS-1210-L2%26WT.mc_ev=click">The 10 best books of 2010</a></li>
